# Frontend – React conventions

- Use React Router for navigation; keep route components in `src/pages/*`.
- Data fetching via TanStack Query; keep API calls in `src/api/*` (create when needed).
- Forms: React Hook Form + Zod; schemas in `src/schemas/*` (create when needed).
- UI: Tailwind + shadcn/ui; shadcn components live in `src/components/ui/*`.
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/utils.ts` for className merging.

